data.description: You'll fall in love with this gorgeous updated ranch on nearly 2 acres of land! New vinyl floors throughout, allergy friendly & freshly painted- move in ready. Gourmet eat in kitchen w/granite counter tops & kitchen appliances to follow (stove, dishwasher & microwave). Family room with cozy fireplace. Spacious primary suite with dual vanities & walk in closet. Queen sized secondary bedrooms & full guest bathroom. Enjoy your morning coffee or tea on the front or rear porch, there are endless options. Massive lot suited for play and/or outdoor entertainment. Side entry 2 car garage. Hurry, this is a steal of a deal!
